caption: Join us on September 26th from 4:00-6:00pm at the Donald Burwash Dining Room, 2nd floor West Wing of Hart House, for an engaging Ethiopian cultural event! Enjoy traditional Ethiopian food and coffee as we come together to explore Ethiopia’s heritage. Hosted by the Cultural Exchange Society and ACTED, this event will highlight the rich traditions of Ethiopia and offer a meaningful opportunity to connect with important cultural and humanitarian themes. We look forward to seeing you there! 🇪🇹🤝🌎
